  "id": "api/core/EventEmitter",
  "title": "EventEmitter",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"page-actions\">\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/event_emitter.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L10-L122\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.0.0/packages/core/src/event_emitter.ts#L10-L122\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/EventEmitter\", \"name\": \"EventEmitter\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"eventemitter\">EventEmitter<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/EventEmitter#eventemitter\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label class\">class</label>\n    \n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label stable\">stable</label>\n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use by directives and components to emit custom Events.</p>\n<p></p>\n  \n  \n  \n  <section class=\"class-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\nclass <a href=\"api/core/EventEmitter\" class=\"code-anchor\">EventEmitter</a>&#x3C;T> extends <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"\">Subject<t></t></a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/EventEmitter#constructor()\">constructor(isAsync: boolean = false)</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/EventEmitter#__isAsync\">__isAsync: boolean</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/EventEmitter#emit\">emit(value?: T)</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/EventEmitter#subscribe\">subscribe(generatorOrNext?: any, error?: any, complete?: any): any</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n\n  \n  \n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/EventEmitter#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"examples\">Examples<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/EventEmitter#examples\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">In the following example, <code>Zippy</code> alternatively emits <code>open</code> and <code>close</code> events when its\ntitle gets clicked:</p>\n<code-example>\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'zippy',\n  template: `\n  &#x3C;div class=\"zippy\">\n    &#x3C;div (click)=\"toggle()\">Toggle&#x3C;/div>\n    &#x3C;div [hidden]=\"!visible\">\n      &#x3C;ng-content>&#x3C;/ng-content>\n    &#x3C;/div>\n &#x3C;/div>`})\nexport class Zippy {\n  visible: boolean = true;\n  @<a href=\"api/core/Output\" class=\"code-anchor\">Output</a>() open: <a href=\"api/core/EventEmitter\" class=\"code-anchor\">EventEmitter</a>&#x3C;any> = new <a href=\"api/core/EventEmitter\" class=\"code-anchor\">EventEmitter</a>();\n  @<a href=\"api/core/Output\" class=\"code-anchor\">Output</a>() close: <a href=\"api/core/EventEmitter\" class=\"code-anchor\">EventEmitter</a>&#x3C;any> = new <a href=\"api/core/EventEmitter\" class=\"code-anchor\">EventEmitter</a>();\n\n  toggle() {\n    this.visible = !this.visible;\n    if (this.visible) {\n      this.open.emit(null);\n    } else {\n      this.close.emit(null);\n    }\n  }\n}\n</code-example>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">The events payload can be accessed by the parameter <code>$event</code> on the components output event\nhandler:</p>\n<code-example>\n&#x3C;zippy (open)=\"onOpen($event)\" (close)=\"onClose($event)\">&#x3C;/zippy>\n</code-example>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">Uses Rx.Observable but provides an adapter to make it work as specified here:\n<a href=\"https://github.com/jhusain/observable-spec\">https://github.com/jhusain/observable-spec</a></p>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">Once a reference implementation of the spec is available, switch to it.</p>\n\n</section>\n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n  <h2 id=\"constructor\">Constructor<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/EventEmitter#constructor\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <a id=\"constructor()\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table constructor\">\n  \n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Creates an instance of <a href=\"api/core/EventEmitter\"><code>EventEmitter</code></a>, which depending on <code>isAsync</code>,\ndelivers events synchronously or asynchronously.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">constructor(isAsync: boolean = false)</code-example>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">Parameters</h4>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table constructor-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"constructor-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>isAsync</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      <p translation-origin=\"off\">      By default, events are delivered synchronously (default value: <code>false</code>).\nSet to <code>true</code> for asynchronous event delivery.</p>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">      Optional. Default is <code>false</code>.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n  \n<section class=\"instance-properties\">\n  <h2 id=\"properties\">Properties<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/EventEmitter#properties\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table properties-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr><th>Property</th><th>Type</th><th>Description</th></tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n    \n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td><a id=\"__isAsync\"></a>__isAsync</td>\n        <td><label class=\"property-type-label\"><code>boolean</code></label></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          \n          \n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    \n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n\n  \n\n<section class=\"instance-methods\">\n  <h2 id=\"methods\">Methods<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/EventEmitter#methods\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n    <a id=\"emit\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table instance-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th><h3 id=\"emit\">\n    emit()\n    \n  <a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/EventEmitter#emit\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3></th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    \n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">emit(value?: T)</code-example>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters-1\">Parameters</h4>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table instance-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>value</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-origin=\"off\">Type: <code>T</code>.</p>\n      <p translation-origin=\"off\">Optional. Default is <code>undefined</code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n    <a id=\"subscribe\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table instance-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th><h3 id=\"subscribe\">\n    subscribe()\n    \n  <a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/EventEmitter#subscribe\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3></th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    \n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">subscribe(generatorOrNext?: any, error?: any, complete?: any): any</code-example>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters-2\">Parameters</h4>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table instance-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>generatorOrNext</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-origin=\"off\">Type: <code>any</code>.</p>\n      <p translation-origin=\"off\">Optional. Default is <code>undefined</code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>error</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-origin=\"off\">Type: <code>any</code>.</p>\n      <p translation-origin=\"off\">Optional. Default is <code>undefined</code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>complete</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-origin=\"off\">Type: <code>any</code>.</p>\n      <p translation-origin=\"off\">Optional. Default is <code>undefined</code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">Returns</h4>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>any</code></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/Directive\n - api/core/NgZone\n - api/forms/FormControlDirective\n - api/forms/FormControlName\n - api/forms/FormGroupDirective\n - api/forms/NgForm\n - api/forms/NgModel\n - api/http/XHRConnection\n - api/http/testing/MockBackend\n - api/http/testing/MockConnection\n - api/platform-webworker/MessageBus\n - api/platform-webworker/MessageBusSink\n - api/platform-webworker/MessageBusSource\n - api/router/RouterOutlet\n - api/upgrade/static/UpgradeComponent\n - api/upgrade/static/downgradeComponent\n - guide/cheatsheet\n - guide/component-interaction\n - guide/elements\n - guide/hierarchical-dependency-injection\n - guide/observables-in-angular\n - guide/styleguide\n - guide/template-syntax\n - guide/testing\n - guide/upgrade\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/EventEmitter#__isAsync\n - api/core/EventEmitter#constructor\n - api/core/EventEmitter#constructor()\n - api/core/EventEmitter#description\n - api/core/EventEmitter#emit\n - api/core/EventEmitter#eventemitter\n - api/core/EventEmitter#examples\n - api/core/EventEmitter#methods\n - api/core/EventEmitter#properties\n - api/core/EventEmitter#subscribe\n - api/core/Output\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/event_emitter.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L10-L122\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.0.0/packages/core/src/event_emitter.ts#L10-L122\n - https://github.com/jhusain/observable-spec\n-->"
